---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import BackToHome from '../components/BackToHome.astro';
import PageNav from '../components/PageNav.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Where to Buy" pageColor="#FF4081">
    <Header />
    
    <main class="main-content">
      <PageHeader 
        title="Where to Buy" 
        color="#FF4081" 
        textColor="white"
      />
      
      <div class="content-container">
        <Breadcrumbs current="Where to Buy" />
        <p>Most Bitcoiners recommend buying bitcoin from a bitcoin only exchange. You can search for <strong class="page-colored-strong">"bitcoin only exchanges"</strong> on the internet to find options in your country. Bitcoiners recommend bitcoin only exchanges because of their focus on providing a safe and secure Bitcoin experience.</p>
        <p>Here are some options available in the US:</p>
        
        <div class="exchange-cards">
          <a href="https://strike.me/" class="exchange-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <div class="card-header">
              <h3>Strike</h3>
              <span class="card-badge">Bitcoin Only</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-description">Lightning-fast Bitcoin purchases with no fees. Built for Bitcoin payments and savings.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-url">strike.me</span>
              <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://river.com/" class="exchange-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <div class="card-header">
              <h3>River Financial</h3>
              <span class="card-badge">Bitcoin Only</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-description">Bitcoin-only financial services with institutional-grade security and custody.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-url">river.com</span>
              <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://www.swanbitcoin.com/" class="exchange-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <div class="card-header">
              <h3>Swan Bitcoin</h3>
              <span class="card-badge">Bitcoin Only</span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-description">Dollar-cost averaging made simple. Automated Bitcoin purchases with low fees.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-url">www.swanbitcoin.com</span>
              <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <BackToHome />
      </div>
      <PageNav />
    </main>

    <style>
      .content-container {
        background: #111;
        border: 1px solid #444;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      
      p {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .exchange-cards {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      
      .exchange-card {
        background: #111;
        border: 1px solid #444;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fff;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        display: block;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }
      
      .exchange-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        border-color: #F7931A;
      }
      
      .card-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      
      .card-header h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .card-badge {
        background: var(--page-color, #FF4081);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        margin-left: 0.75rem;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      
      .card-description {
        color: #e0e0e0;
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      .card-footer {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      
      .card-url {
        color: #aaa;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      
      .card-arrow {
        color: #FF4081;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .exchange-cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 1.5rem;
          max-width: 600px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
        }
      }
    </style>
</BaseLayout>
